# Sprint 232 — TDD red state capture

Date: 2026-05-07
Command: `cargo test --manifest-path src-tauri/Cargo.toml --lib build_default_order_clause`
Pre-implementation tests file: src-tauri/src/db/postgres/queries.rs (mod tests, Sprint 232 block).
Helper not yet implemented at this point — the tests reference
`build_default_order_clause` which does not exist in the source. Compile
fails with E0425 (cannot find function in this scope), which is the
deliberate RED signal: the contract for the new free function is
fixed by the tests before the implementation is written.

