---

The 6 missing-function errors map 1:1 to the 6 new test cases (one
assertion per case). The remaining 5 errors (E0412 / E0422 / E0425
referenced in the summary) are the test helpers' references to the
helper symbol cascading through the call sites; they all resolve once
`build_default_order_clause` is introduced.

Next step: implement `build_default_order_clause` as a `pub(super) fn`
in `queries.rs` and wire it into `query_table_data` so that the
fallback emits when the user-supplied parsing path leaves
`order_clause` empty. Re-run the same command for GREEN.
